    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226430/extras/7c56dde1faeba6061a63bedefbd0b177.poster.avif?t=1768814723\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226430/extras/7c56dde1faeba6061a63bedefbd0b177.webm?t=1768814723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226430/extras/7c56dde1faeba6061a63bedefbd0b177.mp4?t=1768814723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自《死亡与税赋》制作团队的重磅新作 ——《奇巧匠：手工经商模拟》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 在一个宁静的港口小镇，成为一名珠宝匠或铁匠。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 自定义角色 —— 蛾人、精灵，或是猫猫！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 结识形形色色的人物，并影响他们的生活。你的选择将改变故事走向！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 养一只可爱的枭猫宠物！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 放松身心，享受手工制作的乐趣～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 制作亮晶晶的东西 ✧ ⋆ ˙ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 制作更多亮晶晶的东西 ⋆ ˙ ✧ + * ˙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 制作不太亮晶晶但很<strong>不详</strong>的东西</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 全程配音</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 共计 11 个游戏日，分支剧情贯穿其中，一周目约 5～7 小时 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 丰富的可重复游玩内容（多个角色背景、路线专属人物、随机客人与可回收材料） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 原创配乐，使用真实的民俗乐器录制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 独一无二的手工制作模拟！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226430/extras/188d2e621a1cd347e5da0d63fdacd8d3.avif?t=1768814723\" width=616 height=190 /></span></p>",
